PrecisCROW BENEFIT (CENTRAL WESTERN RAILWAY CORPORATION) ORDER NO. 4 - which provides that the "Crow Benefit" payable to the aforementioned railroad in respect of the crop years 1992/93 through 1998/99 shall be reduced by an amount equal to the amount payable to the railroad under an Agreement made pursuant to the Western Grain Transportation Act.

precis:
CROW BENEFIT (CENTRAL WESTERN RAILWAY CORPORATION) ORDER NO. 4 - which
provides that the "Crow Benefit" payable to the aforementioned railroad
in respect of the crop years 1992/93 through 1998/99 shall be reduced by
an amount equal to the amount payable to the railroad under an Agreement
made pursuant to the Western Grain Transportation Act.
